doalarm 0.1.7 (14 Dec 2001)
Copyright 2001, M.J. Pomraning <mjp@pilcrow.madison.wi.us>
README 

INTRO:

doalarm's basic operation is equivalent to:

  $ perl -e 'alarm shift @ARGV; exec @ARGV' 5 some_command ...

Especially useful for time limiting otherwise blocking commands.


INSTALL:

make
make install


BUGS:

Bug reports to mjp@pilcrow.madison.wi.us.


